#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.cbrt.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.cbrt"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.cbrt.cbrt:1 of
msgid "Return the cube-root of an tensor, element-wise."
msgstr "返回一个张量的立方根，按元素计算。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.cbrt.cbrt of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.cbrt.cbrt:3 of
msgid "The values whose cube-roots are required."
msgstr "需要计算立方根的值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.cbrt.cbrt:5 of
msgid ""
"A location into which the result is stored. If provided, it must have a "
"shape that the inputs broadcast to. If not provided or `None`, a freshly-"
"allocated tensor is returned. A tuple (possible only as a keyword "
"argument) must have length equal to the number of outputs."
msgstr ""
"用于存储结果的位置。如果提供，其形状必须可以广播到输入。如果未提供或为 `"
"None`，则返回一个新分配的张量。元组（仅可作为关键字参数）的长度必须等于"
"输出的数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.cbrt.cbrt:10 of
msgid ""
"Values of True indicate to calculate the ufunc at that position, values "
"of False indicate to leave the value in the output alone."
msgstr "为 True 的值表示在该位置计算 ufunc，为 False 的值表示保留输出中的值不变。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.cbrt.cbrt of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.cbrt.cbrt:15 of
msgid ""
"**y** -- An tensor of the same shape as `x`, containing the cube cube-"
"root of each element in `x`. If `out` was provided, `y` is a reference to"
" it."
msgstr ""
"**y** -- 与 `x` 形状相同的张量，包含 `x` 中每个元素的立方根。如果提供了 `"
"out`，则 `y` 是其引用。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.cbrt.cbrt of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

